Subject: [PATCH 21/21] gitk: bring window to front on launch

This fixes gitk launching in the background on macOS Sequoia.

Git-gui also calls this unconditionally on all platforms, so it can't be bad. :)
---
 gitk-git/gitk | 4 +---
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/gitk-git/gitk b/gitk-git/gitk
index c04845bb1c..79df063c19 100755
--- a/gitk-git/gitk
+++ b/gitk-git/gitk
@@ -12771,9 +12771,7 @@ if {[info exists permviews]} {
     }
 }
 
-if {[tk windowingsystem] eq "win32"} {
-    focus -force .
-}
+focus -force .
 
 getcommits {}
 
